author: billbarker
msg: Set the path elements after setting the Request attributes.

The 'hrequest' wraps the 'wrequest' in most (non-trivial, where it doesn't matter) cases, so if the Wrapper doesn't override the path-element methods, previously we got the wrong attribute values.  If the Wrapper does override the path-element methods, than this is no more broken than before.
